Title: Fujitsu High Static Pressure Duct ARYG90LHTA R410A High Static Duct Indoor Unit
Description: Employing all DC inverter technology, the Fujitsu Big Duct indoor unit's high static duct system offers high levels of efficiency and performance along with simplified installation. Compact and lightweight, the indoor chassis is designed to reduce the amount of turbulent airflow, meaning quieter operation. This smart air conditioning unit has cooling outputs of up to 22kW and heating outputs up to 27kW.
